'From Squeak2.8alpha of 4 February 2000 [latest update: #2052] on 3 May 2000 at 11:16:39 pm'!"Change Set:		031MagMorphFix-smaDate:			4 May 2000Author:			Stefan Matthias AustA fix to a bug introduced in 2030, now MagnifierMorph and FishEyeMorph should work again."!!MagnifierMorph methodsFor: 'magnifying' stamp: 'sma 5/1/2000 19:34'!sourcePoint	"If we are being dragged use our center, otherwise use pointer position"	^(trackPointer not or: [owner notNil and: [owner isHandMorph]])		ifTrue: [self center]		ifFalse: [self currentHand lastEvent cursorPoint]! !